<br />
Shadow: Just throw together some Uruk-hai.     </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Basically, this deck revolves around discarding Hobbits and moving twice. Exert Frodo or add a burden to pitch your hobbits into the discard pile, then jerk them out in the regroup phase. Wound minions with Defend it and Hope, wound them some more with Aragorn and Faramir, then finish them off when you move with Aragorn&#39;s text. THis deck probably won&#39;t win any tournements, but it&#39;s good for beginners to get them used to some of the strategies. <br />
Have fun!  </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
